g.text: Then up on a nearby roof is the God of Love, training his arrow on us both…

g.text: That image will never leave my mind now. Thanks!

g.text: I’ve been trying to find the moment, you know. I can’t.

g.title: j879003892
g.text: I’ve been trying to find the moment, you know. I can’t.

g.title: j799228362
g.text: The moment when I realized I was in love with you, of course.

g.title: j2280587920
g.text: I remember thinking ‘well, this is bloody inconvenient, Eleanor, now you’re bound to make a complete fool of yourself.’

g.title: j3615612746
g.text: The moment when I realized that my life had been changed by you. When you had wriggled your way into my heart and become family.

g.title: j315582716
g.text: But not when, or what we were doing.

g.title: j2612032714
g.text: I suppose I should say thank you. For listening to me. For entertaining all these wild fancies of mine. And, most importantly, for being my friend.

g.title: j3879959900
g.text: I... oh. I'm not ready for that kind of commitment... I'm sorry.

g.title: j3466183084
g.text: It doesn’t matter. I love you.

g.title: j1426273667
g.text: My Drifter. You fell into my life and turned everything on its head. Of all the choices you could have made, you chose me. You left me wide-eyed and wonderstruck.

g.title: j2083390889
g.text: What's the bloody point? I ask you. What is the bloody POINT??

g.title: j166507962
g.text: Can I interest you in some enthusiastic kissing, with an option to proceed to rampant sexual intercourse?

g.title: j2175073977
g.text: Let’s start with kissing and see where we end up.

g.title: j4115610679
g.text: Let’s take it slow. Kissing is plenty.

g.title: j2963035853
g.text: Mmm. Let's feel our way forward, then. Sounds perfect.

g.title: j1160264275
g.text: And right there is the secret to making this work. Communication. If kissing is what you want, then kissing you shall have.
